Since I moved out here, my goal was to get the rest of my family out here with me. I was scared of how long it would take, if I'd have enough money to help, what the process was going to be like, pero mira! A little over a year, both my sister and I finally did it!!! We couldn't have done it without the help of our realtors Monica and Laura @ realtor_monicasinger ! Im so thankful for this and couldn't have done it without you perras either!! In this video we surprise my parents with the home and get their reaction!
